---

<section class="welcome">
  <div class="welcome-content">
    <div class="welcome-text">
      <h2>Bienvenida a Nuestra Tienda ✨</h2>
      <p>
        Descubre una colección cuidadosamente seleccionada de blusas hermosas, 
        cómodas y perfectas para cualquier momento de tu vida. Cada prenda está 
        hecha con amor y dedicación.
      </p>
      <div class="welcome-features">
        <div class="feature">
          <span class="icon">🎁</span>
          <span>Envío gratis en compras mayores a $50</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <span class="icon">💳</span>
          <span>Pagos seguros y fáciles</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <span class="icon">♻️</span>
          <span>Devoluciones sin preocupaciones</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="welcome-image">
      <div class="floating-emoji">👗</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .welcome {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8) 0%, rgba(245, 241, 232, 0.8) 100%);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    border: 2px solid rgba(232, 213, 196, 0.6);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .welcome-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .welcome-text h2 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    color: #5a4a42;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .welcome-text p {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    color: #8a7a72;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .welcome-features {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #5a4a42;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .icon {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    min-width: 2rem;
  }

  .welcome-image {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .floating-emoji {
    font-size: 8rem;
    animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(5deg);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .welcome {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .welcome-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .welcome-image {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
